<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi {!Lead.FirstName},<br></span></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>As I’ve not heard back from any of my previous attempts to provide you with a quote for your business insurance, I will now be closing your records on our system.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>However, if you are&nbsp;<b>interested in proceeding with your quote</b>&nbsp;at any time in the future -&nbsp;</span><a href="https://calendly.com/d/cm3g-k74-js2/kingsbridge-insurance-call-back" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><b>book a call with me</b></a><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Alternatively, you can always give me a ring on&nbsp;</span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808 740</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><font style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</font></p>]]></td>
